<div class='span12'>
<h2>An Unsuitable Genre for a Woman in the Global South? (Promotionsprojekt)</h2>
<h3>The Representation of Women and Space in Contemporary Latin American and Indian Crime Fiction </h3>
<hr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
<h4>Allgemeine Angaben</h4>
<dl class='attribute_listing'>
<dt>Projektbeginn</dt>
